{{nonsense}}Slumgullion is a stew of meat and vegetables, a beverage made watery, such as weak coffee or tea, a reddish muddy deposit in mining sluices, and a sperm whaleman's term, roughly equivalent to the right whaleman's "gurry," which, according to Herman Melville, "designates the dark, glutinous substance which is scraped off the back of the Greenland or Right Whale, and much of which covers the decks of those inferior souls who hunt that ignoble Leviathan."